Given a warrior
  Given a direction
    When there is a wall
      Change direction
    When there is a captive
      Save the captive
    When there is an enemy
      Attack the enemy
    When the path is clear
      When taking damage and low on health
        Walk backward
      When at partial health and facing bacward
        Rest up
      When at full health
        Walk forward


A warrior is low on health when:
- the warrior will die before backing out of combat

A warrior is taking damage when:
- the health for the current turn is less than the health for the previous turn
